item.description:
@Phaze_One wrote:

[quote=“usman555, post:3, topic:340455”][quote author=bello33 link=topic=436827.msg3209514#msg3209514 date=1274116452]
This project will be made for some other players that always cant find what they want this project might include website
it will include for sure webclient. Contact me at god-pureage-scape@live.com to apply for job here , not paying
[/quote]

I’ll be a coder that adds npcs, shops and commands. Nothing else.

Here’s a piece of my work. Let’s say you are currently adding a money command that gives 999m, and only for owners

if(command.startsWith(“money”) && playerRights == 3) {
addItem(995, 999999999);
sM(“free 999m”);
}[/quote]

Wow man, I wish I could do the things you do.
